		<h1 class="headerStyle">Internet Radio Privacy Policy:</h1>
			<p>Internet Radio ("Internet Radio") operates Internet Radio and may operate other websites. It is Internet Radio Radio policy to respect your privacy regarding any information we may collect while operating our websites.</p>
		<h2>Website Visitors</h2>
